        "content": "<div id=\"content\"><div class=\"section\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Upload a maximum of 5 videos to include them in the TV! Videos need to be: <br>> In .mp4 or .webm format <br>> In horizontal orientation <br>> Less than 4-ish minutes long per video (Due to Minecraft's limitation) <br>> You need to wait until the preview video is playable before you can download the Addon! <br><table><thead><tr><th>Video Source</th><th>Preview</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><label for=\"upload1\" class=\"uploadButton\">Upload 1</label><input type=\"file\" accept=\".mp4, .webm\" id=\"upload1\" class=\"fileTrigger\"></td><td><video class=\"previewVideo\" id=\"upload1video\" controls></video><div id=\"upload1info\" class=\"info\"><p class=\"childMessage\">Message:</p><progress id=\"upload1progress\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\" class=\"childProgress\"></progress></div></td></tr><tr><td><label for=\"upload2\" class=\"uploadButton\">Upload 2</label><input type=\"file\" accept=\".mp4, .webm\" id=\"upload2\" class=\"fileTrigger\"></td><td><video class=\"previewVideo\" id=\"upload2video\" controls></video><div id=\"upload2info\" class=\"info\"><p class=\"childMessage\">Message:</p><progress id=\"upload1progress\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\" class=\"childProgress\"></progress></div></td></tr><tr><td><label for=\"upload3\" class=\"uploadButton\">Upload 3</label><input type=\"file\" accept=\".mp4, .webm\" id=\"upload3\" class=\"fileTrigger\"></td><td><video class=\"previewVideo\" id=\"upload3video\" controls></video><div id=\"upload3info\" class=\"info\"><p class=\"childMessage\">Message:</p><progress id=\"upload1progress\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\" class=\"childProgress\"></progress></div></td></tr><tr><td><label for=\"upload4\" class=\"uploadButton\">Upload 4</label><input type=\"file\" accept=\".mp4, .webm\" id=\"upload4\" class=\"fileTrigger\"></td><td><video class=\"previewVideo\" id=\"upload4video\" controls></video><div id=\"upload4info\" class=\"info\"><p class=\"childMessage\">Message:</p><progress id=\"upload1progress\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\" class=\"childProgress\"></progress></div></td></tr><tr><td><label for=\"upload5\" class=\"uploadButton\">Upload 5</label><input type=\"file\" accept=\".mp4, .webm\" id=\"upload5\" class=\"fileTrigger\"></td><td><video class=\"previewVideo\" id=\"upload5video\" controls></video><div id=\"upload5info\" class=\"info\"><p class=\"childMessage\">Message:</p><progress id=\"upload1progress\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\" class=\"childProgress\"></progress></div></td></tr></tbody></table><br><br><label for=\"devMode\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"devMode\"><span> Enable Dev Mode (Do not enable unless instructed to do so)</span></label><br><br><p class=\"devDebug\" id=\"debugMessage\">Debug message:</p><div id=\"imageContainer\" class=\"devDebug\"></div></div></div>"
